state animation off
action kCreateCylinder
select

section Stage The stage
state video on

caption .5 .15 3 The circular stage is where models are placed
wait 3

moveover Stage 0 0 -.145
state cursor on
caption .5 .15 3 It can be rotated and scaled;to change the model view
drag .1 0 2
moveover Stage 1 0 -.145
drag 0 -.05 2

caption .5 .15 2 Shift-click or double-click it to reset it
moveover Stage .1 0 -.145
state mod on
click
state mod off
wait 1
